BFN 

  [Text] His Majesty King Husayn received German Labor 
Minister Norbert Bluem at the Royal Court today. His majesty 
stressed Jordan's position on the peace process in the region, 
and the need to reach a just and comprehensive solution that 
guarantees the Arab and Islamic rights as stipulated in the 
international resolutions. 
  Norbert Bluem praised His Majesty King Husayn's wise 
leadership and the firm and balanced Jordanian policy toward 
various regional and international issues. He expressed his 
country's concern about promoting cooperation between the two 
countries. 
  Attending the meeting were al-Sharif Zayd Bin-Shakir, chief 
of the Royal Hashemite Court; Khalid al-Ghizawi, labor minister; 
and the German ambassador in Amman. 

